The reason simones threads turn to Yobama is because she is attacking Rick Warren as if he is responsible for anything the Ugandan Government does. Simones link attempts to link Warren to this legislation because of his relationship with a Ugandan Pastor, but according to this Newsweek article, Warren broke ranks with this Pastor back in 07 precisely because of these attitudes and opinions of his. And notice the date of this article, it is very current. Pastor Rick Warren Responds to Proposed Antigay Ugandan Legislation - The Human Condition Blog - Newsweek.com